ems, this just increases. <br><br>People in general need to be on the lookout for kids in need of a kind word, a word of encouragement, constructive feedback. Every little bit helps. When things like this happen, it is a sign of society deteriorating one piece at a time, and that is where we need to focus to fix it. Placing micro blame is no way to address and help a macro problem.<br><br>By the way, I favor intellectual discipline and deprivement as a reward for negative behavior, but there are extreme cases and situations when a warmed butt gets attention more than anything else can. I haven't been spanked since I was 8. Why? I figured out what caused it and stopped doing f*cked up sh*t. I don't condone physical abuse, but I know the difference, and I think people just waiting to be the hero of some little boy getting his butt smacked because he is cussing at his mother in the grocery store are worthless. <br><br>Now that I am kinda getting off topic.../rant off. <p><BR><center>Whytspirit of the Nexus</center> <center>Wife to Hallace Nexusmaximus</center><center>(not Wubwub :p)</center><center>Mystic of Dark Brigade</center><center><img src="http://www.etherealms.com/whyt/WhytsSpearSm.gif"></center><center><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=190375" target="blank">My Goodies</a></center><center><BR>It's not about the loot...It's about the challenge!</center></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub54.ezboard.com/uchatwoodnoname.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Chatwood noname</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Froglok Guk Knight</span><br>  Posts: 7<br> <font color=#00CCFF>(4/29/02 11:35:18 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub54.ezboard.com/fquelliousquaterstherebirthfrm13.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=301.topic&index=17>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: OT- Another School Shooting</span><hr size